results.cleanName: Speed Duel Match of the Millennium Starter Deck 1st Edition

extendedData.name: Description
extendedData.value:
Each Yu-Gi-Oh! TCG Speed Duel: Match of the Millennium Starter Deck contains:
• 1 x 31-Card Yugi Deck
• 1 x 31-Card Pegasus Deck
• 4 Skill Cards (2 for Yugi and 2 for Pegasus)
• 2 Ultra Rare variant cards

(This card is always treated as a "Toon" card.)
Cannot be Normal Summoned/Set. Cannot be Special Summoned unless you control a face-up "Toon World". Must first be Special Summoned (from your hand) by Tributing the same number of monsters needed for a Tribute Summon (normally 2). This card cannot attack the turn it is Special Summoned. You must pay 500 Life Points to declare an attack with this monster. If "Toon World" on the field is destroyed, destroy this card. This card can attack your opponent directly, unless they control a Toon Monster. If they do control one, this card must target a Toon Monster for its attacks.

Activate this Skill during your Main Phase, while you control "Black Luster Soldier" or "Magician of Black Chaos" that you Ritual Summoned this turn.
• While you control "Black Luster Soldier", it cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Skill, also once per turn, if your opponent activates a Trap Card, draw 1 card immediately after it resolves.
• While you control "Magician of Black Chaos", it cannot be destroyed by your opponent's Spell effects, also if your "Magician of Black Chaos" destroys a monster by battle, add 1 Spell from your GY to your hand.

• If it attacks a Defense Position monster, inflict piercing battle damage. Once per turn, if it inflicts battle damage with this Skill, draw 2 cards, then discard 1 card.
